{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534504211&di=862e62e9971d4f9da6c4ad745876eb75&src=http%3A%2F%2Ff.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F2e2eb9389b504fc208f22529eddde71190ef6d69.jpg","summary":"重庆旅游职业学院(Chongqing Vocational Institute of Tourism)，简称“重庆旅游职院”，坐落在渝东南地区中心城市和武陵山片区中心城市——重庆市黔江区，是重庆市人民政府设立、教育部备案的一所公办旅游高等院校。该校是中央财政专项补助资金“支持高职学校提升专业服务产业发展能力”项目院校、重庆市旅游职业教育现代学徒制人才培养模式试点高校、重庆市“大学生创新创业训练计划”项目院校、重庆市“雨露计划·职教扶贫”项目院校。截至2014年6月，学院占地面积500余亩，拥有教职工180余人，在校生3000余人。设有导游、景区开发与管理、旅游管理、旅行社经营与管理、酒店管理、城市园林、舞蹈表演、音乐表演、烹饪工艺与营养等16个专科专业，涵盖“吃住行游购娱”等旅游行业需求。","tags":["综合类","专科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"2010","所在地区":"重庆市黔江区舟白街道学府一路一号","院校隶属":"重庆市"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504211&di=92d456ffac6453fb9731f241987f033e&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3818032215%2C935951367%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504211&di=2815b9f600e3c04f143d1e171de3f519&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3758176324%2C922540085%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504211&di=b7dcf84e985d7918c3cad5c2891dce69&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3544351770%2C602697033%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504211&di=0ec53186ee12d393779cd84e9bffabe6&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3396314591%2C3887440678%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504211&di=f4f3f3d1b2fd195142d203478fb2b21a&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3743511043%2C4014091762%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9